Dialogs.Dialog: ▲主人公＊▲. About what I call you...
▲新主人公▲... Can I call you like this？
Yeah, it's okay to call me that.
Really？ Now we sound more like lovers, don't you think？
Hmm... How about trying something else...？
Isn't it fine the way it is now？
▲新主人公▲. I just wanted to try this name. How is it？
Yeah, it's okay to call me that.
Hmm... How about trying something else...？
▲主人公＊▲. Eh？ This doesn't sound that bad.
Impossible. Don't get ahead of yourself！
Isn't it fine the way it is now？
Yeah, it's okay to call me that.
Yay！ It's a little embarrassing, isn't it？
Hmm... How about trying something else...？
▲主人公＊▲. Hehe... I'll call you this.
Isn't it fine the way it is now？
Really？ I see... I got it.
If I call you this way, what do you think？
I see. I just thought that you might like this.
(Well, since she asked, I'd better choose what I like...)
I'd rather go with ▲新主人公▲. How's that？
What was that？ So weird. Anyway, if you like it, I'll call you like that.
▲主人公＊▲. Hmm. So, you like it like this, huh？
Huh？ You like something like that？
(Tsk. So, this is not good, huh...？)
Hey, you want to be called like this, right？
As I thought. I have no choice.
(Well, since she asked, I'd better choose what I like...)
I'd rather go with ▲新主人公▲. How's that？
▲主人公＊▲. I say it specially for you, okay？
Ah... You take it seriously？ I was just joking！ Hahaha！
(Tsk. So, this is not good, huh...？)
No good？ You don't like this name？
Really？ I'm glad I tried calling you like that.
(Well, since she asked, I'd better choose what I like...)
I'd rather go with ▲新主人公▲. How's that？
Hey, I just tried calling you. It's so embarrassing when you become that happy.
Um... That's probably not good, right？
(Tsk. So, this is not good, huh...？)
I see... Well, don't think of me as a weirdo, okay？
(Should I try changing what I call ▲小早川＊▲...？)
I should keep it the same
Really？ Then I'll call you this from now on.
(Should I try changing what I call ▲小早川＊▲...？)
I should keep it the same
(Should I try changing what I call ▲小早川＊▲...？)
I should keep it the same
So, I should stop calling you like that？
